title: Kylie Jenner Rocks the World's Largest Coat at New York Fashion Week
text: Kylie Jenner Rocks the World’s Largest Coat at New York Fashion Week by Rachel McRady 4:24 AM PST, February 13, 2017 Photo: Instagram It’s cold out there! Kylie Jenner is known for showing skin, but on Sunday, the 19-year-old reality star opted to bundle up instead. While visiting with German designer pal Philipp Plein, Jenner rocked an enormous oversized black down coat. A photo posted by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Feb 12, 2017 at 5:42pm PST Plein also posted the pic, writing, “@kyliejenner The countdown is on #LetsMakeNYFWgreatAgain #NeighborHoodKingsNEWYORK.” The designer also shared a pic of model Sofia Richie rocking a black lace-up crop top and matching undies with a fur hoodie over top. Richie teased that she will be strutting her stuff in the Plein runway show on Monday. A photo posted by Philipp Plein (@philippplein78) on Feb 12, 2017 at 1:31pm PST “@philippplein78 runway tomorrow! Can’t wait for you to see,” she captioned one Instagram shot. Jenner and Richie’s paths have been crossing a lot during NYFW. The pair sat front row at the Jeremy Scott show over the weekend, goofing off on each other’s social media accounts. A photo posted by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Feb 12, 2017 at 4:40pm PST The cosmetics queen has been keeping busy while on the East Coast. On Sunday she visited her pop-up shop in Manhattan, sporting an all-denim ensemble. “Spend it all at the pop up!!” she captioned a selfie wearing a belted oversized jean jacket. For more of Jenner’s recent NYFW antics, watch the clip below! RELATED SLIDESHOW
